# KERNEL: contents of p2 before changes
# KERNEL: THE VALUE OF A IS 10
# KERNEL: contents of p1 after changes
# KERNEL: THE VALUE OF A IS 10
# KERNEL: contents of p2 after changes
# KERNEL: THE VALUE OF A IS 57 */
